

<style>
.photoContainer {
  width: 100%;
  height: 40vh;
  text-align: center;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-top: 0px;
}

.postframe {
  padding: 3vh;
  margin-top: -10vh;
  background-color: white;
  border-radius: 3px;
}

.containerposition {
  position: relative;
  margin-top: -2vh;
}

#my_iFrame{
height: 400px;
width: 100%;
max-width: 800px;

}


.iframe-container-post {
  overflow: hidden;
  padding-top: 56.25%;
  position: relative;

}

.iframe-container-post iframe {
   border: 0;
   height: 100%;
   left: 0;
   position: absolute;
   top: 0;
   width: 100%;
}

/* 4x3 Aspect Ratio */
.iframe-container-4x3-post {
  padding-top: 95%;
}

.background-img {
  background: rgb(2,0,36);
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(2,0,36,0.9) 0%, rgba(58,57,131,0.8164040616246498) 52%, rgba(51,137,154,0.9) 100%);
  border-radius: 3px;
  object-fit: fill
}

.link-style-obrigado {
  color: black;
  font-size: 5vh;
  padding: 2vh;
  margin-top: 0vh;
}

</style>


<div
style="
background: #0f0c29;  /* fallback for old browsers */
background: -webkit-linear-gradient(to right, #24243e, #302b63, #0f0c29);  /* Chrome 10-25, Safari 5.1-6 */
background: linear-gradient(to right, #24243e, #302b63, #0f0c29); /* W3C, IE 10+/ Edge, Firefox 16+, Chrome 26+, Opera 12+, Safari 7+ */
">

<div class="photoContainer">
  <img class="background-img" src=<%= @post["photo"] %> alt=<%= @post["title"] %>>
</div>


<div class="container" style="position: relative; margin-top: -15vh;" >



  <div class="postframe">

    <center>

      <%= image_tag "igf-logo.png", height: 90 %>
      <h2 style="font-size: 2vh;" class="hide"><%= @post["date"].html_safe%></h2>
      <h1 style="font-size: 3vh;"><%= @post["title"].html_safe%></h1>
      <hr style="font-size: 1.7vh; margin-top: 0px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.7vh; margin-top: -5px;" class=""><%= @post["date"].html_safe%></h2>
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.7vh; margin-top: -10px;">por Felipe Guimarães | co-fundador do IGF</h2>
      <br>
    </center>


    <% if !@post["video"].nil? %>

      <h3 style="font-size: 2vh; font-style: italic;">Veja o artigo completo:</h3>
      <hr style="margin-top: -0.7vh;">
      <br>
        <% if @post["video"] != " " %>
          <div class="iframe-container-post">
            <iframe src=<%= @post["video"].html_safe%> frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
        <% end %>

      <br>
    <% end %>
    <div style="padding: 3vh;"><%= @post["text"].html_safe%></div>

    <br>
    <br>
    <p style="color: black; margin-bottom: 0vh; font-size: 2vh; font-style: italic;">Gostaria de se tornar um planejador financeiro?</p>
    <hr style="margin-top: 0vh;">

    <center>
    <p style="font-size: 2vh;">Nos acompanhe também nas redes socias, lá você vai encontrar várias <strong>dicas sobre como se tornar um planejador financeiro profissional</strong> e <strong>faturar com seus primeiros clientes</strong></p>
    <div>
      <a href="" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-twitter link-style-obrigado hide"></i></a>
      <a href="" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-linkedin link-style-obrigado hide"></i></a>
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/institutoguiafinanceiro" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-facebook-square link-style-obrigado"></i></a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/igf_planejadores/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-instagram link-style-obrigado"></i></a>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9l5V9TB0gUGjXxVBjQm6tg" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube-square link-style-obrigado"></i></a>
    </center>


    <div class="hide">
      <center>
        <%= link_to inscricoes_encerradas_path do %>
          <div class="btn btn-danger btn-block" style="margin-top: -0.3vh; max-width: 600px;">Quero me tornar um planejador financeiro</div>
        <% end %>
      </center>
    </div>
    <br>


  </div>

  <br>
  <br>
  <div style="background-color: white;">
    <div class="fb-comments" data-href="https://www.institutoguiafinanceiro.com/" data-numposts="10" data-width=""></div>
  </div>

</div>

<br>
<br>
<br>
</div>
